    "caveat": "When installed, initialized and configured as specified in Section 11.1 of the Security Policy",
    "description": "Apricorn’s Aegis Secure Key 3z is a hardware encrypted USB 3.1 memory key. Its software-free design works with any host that supports USB and mass storage compliant. Authentication is performed via the embedded keypad & all CSPs (PINs, encryption keys, etc) never leave the device boundary for improved security. The 3z supports 1 admin and 1 user, has no factory default PINs (requires Force Enrollment upon first use) and offers a variety of features including programmable brute force, recovery PINs, 7-16 digit PIN, auto lock, read only modes, and is compatible with Apricorn’s Aegis Configurator",
